pchangeofhands.pchangeofhand:
The handwriting is very regular, neat and uniform,  characterized by finely shaped, slender and upright letters.
Some distinctive features:
- the letter ለ in the 1st order has the right leg more curved then the left one;
- the letter መ in the 1st and 2nd order has the left loop  resting on the ruled line, bigger than the right one;  
- x-cross with dashes is used a few times, e.g., fol. 57vb l.13.
